# 🎙️ Creative R&D Playground

An active sandbox for documenting enterprise AI insights, creative experiments, and technical deep-dives.

## 📖 Overview

Technology moves on a compounding acceleration curve. I stay ahead of this by actively testing,
sometimes breaking, and creating with emerging tools. This repository serves as a living record of
my explorations, bridging the gap between high-level strategy and hands-on execution.

---

## 🧪 Active Sandboxes

### 📝 [JennAI.blog](https://jennai.blog)

My primary hub for technical writing and recording my observations.

- **Focus:** Enterprise AI insights, generative architecture, and hands-on tutorials.
- **Purpose:** Bridging the gap between high-level engineering strategy and practical application.

---

### 🔊 Synthetic Voice Engineering

Merging a decade-long background in professional voiceover with modern generative tech.

- **Tools:** ElevenLabs API integration.
- **Milestone:** High-fidelity voice clone that has achieved over 164.2k likes in real-world validation — [listen here](https://elevenlabs.io/app/voice-lab/share/6b5293afac57fd085dac3f58c7e8a68be63d0d3dafa32d5ec28c2290e5bd4f20/kddBBBVfGtKWVjCos6yL).
- **Application:** Exploring the future of automated narration, personalized GTM collateral, and
  dynamic voice-driven interfaces.

---

### 🎵 AI-Augmented Music Production

A comprehensive study in hybrid audio production.

- **Tools:** Suno (generative composition), professional Digital Audio Workstations (DAW).
- **Workflow:** Generating and mastering instrumental tracks via Suno, then deploying traditional
  audio engineering and adding vocal performance inside the editor.
- **Goal:** Engineering a seamless harmony between human performance and algorithmic synthesis
  to push the boundaries of pop music production.

